Python is a general-purpose programming language, which means it can be used for many different types of programming and software development tasks. It is one of the most popular programming languages because of its simple syntax, easy readability, and beginner-friendly nature.

Python is used in many fields such as (Application of Python) : 

Web Development –> creating websites and web applications
Software Development –> building desktop applications and tools
Automation –> automating repetitive tasks using scripts
Data Science & Data Analysis –> working with data and generating insights
Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning –> developing smart systems and AI models
Game Development –> creating simple and advanced games
